Fact

Florida & South Dakota didn’t shutdown
Children stayed in School
Businesses stayed open - Disney world stayed open
They didn’t mask up or mandate vaccination

They are no worse then California or New York

All while Florida has the Oldest Population of retirees living there

Former U.S. Digital Service staffer finds fault with South Dakota Vaccine Passport System RFO on podcast due to 'unjustifiable' out-of-context mention of a Cloud Static Site. Get ahead and stay ahead with @BREAKINGGOVTECH.

Black Hills Stock & Rodeo Show in Rapid City, South Dakota ran from Jan. 28 to Feb. 5 with 300k participants. A vaccination booth was set up for COVID, flu & shingles shots. At the end of the event they had vaccinated 12 people. Out of. 300k. Stop claiming you want this to end.

12 vaccinations given at South Dakota rodeo attended by 300,000 ppl over several days, where vaccination rates are tremendously low. An outrageous commentary on the state of 'COVID-affairs' in the U.S. An example of why we can't get out from under this thing.
